<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>INTERVIEW RESCHEDULE NOTICE</title>
</head>

<body
    style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">
    <div
        style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">

        <div style="text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <h2 style="color: #007bff; margin: 0;">INTERVIEW RESCHEDULE NOTICE</h2>
        </div>

        <p>Dear <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>

        <p>We apologize for the inconvenience. Your interview has been moved to a new time.</p>

        <p>Our HR team still warmly invites you to join the interview to discuss your skills and role expectations in detail.</p>

        <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #007bff; margin: 20px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>⏰ Time:</strong> {{time}}</p>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>📍 Format:</strong> Online interview via Google Meet</p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{link}}"
                style="background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px;">
                🎥 Click here to join the meeting
            </a>
        </div>

        <p><em>*Please join on time and check your network, microphone, and camera before the meeting.</em></p>

        <p>If you need support or want to request a different schedule, please reply to this email.</p>

        <br>
        <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>HR Team</strong>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>